{"type": "article", "id": 21471, "title": "蜡烛灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-29T07:33:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 53, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606153734Hbs7zVZ2gKlEFILo.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一款无需插头的灯，也不使用电池。使用时需要在下面的罩子里放上了一个圆形蜡烛，点燃后的热量传递到中间的热电装置，帮助上面的 LED 灯发光。灯的外形像水瓶，外面的透明的罩子也有挡风的作用。蜡烛的照明范围是有限的，设计者却没有取消它，想要保留一种原始的情调，也想以此帮助落后地区照明。这盏灯目前在众筹，<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/525554173/lumir-c-candle-powered-led-lamp\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150955jcVJIBbEk3ZOm6lS.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"818\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150955UtcQT5shugxFv1PN.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"800\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.97799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150955HPwiJjhNZe3EGqos.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"584\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150956bORuwCTN9ivtnmKB.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"454\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150956lICT4c30V6FO1ZrN.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"628\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76772616\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}